ends and Influencing People\" Review |last=Goldman |first=Eric |publisher=[[IGN]] |date=October 7, 2014 |accessdate=January 4, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6VKNzQu3D?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/10/08/marvels-agents-of-shield-making-friends-and-influencing-people-review |archivedate=January 4, 2015 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"April2006Variety\">{{cite news|date=April 27, 2006 |first=Pamela |last=McClintock |title=Marvel Making Deals for Title Wave |url=https://www.variety.com/article/VR1117942193 |work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |accessdate=March 1, 2008 |archivedate=May 1, 2011 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yMj0t8bu?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117942193 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"FergusOstbyIM\">{{cite news |date=April 17, 2008 |last=Jensen |first=Jeff |title=''Iron Man'': Summer's first Marvel? |work=[[Entertainment Weekly]] |url=https://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20192634_3,00.html |accessdate=April 21, 2008 |archivedate=March 28, 2013 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6FSZjS9xS?url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20192634_3,00.html |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NYCC2012\">{{cite web |url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=41604 |title=NYCC: Coulson Lives In Whedon's \"S.H.I.E.L.D.\" |last=Sunu |first=Steven |publisher=[[Comic Book Resources]] |date=October 13, 2012 |accessdate=October 13, 2012 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BONvEhyg?url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=41604 |archivedate=October 13, 2012 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"GreggScreenRantApr2013\">{{cite web|url=https://screenrant.com/agent-coulson-shield-role-avengers-death-return/ |title=Clark Gregg Suggests Coulson\u2019s Return Could Mean \u2018The Avengers\u2019 Were Deceived |last=Nemiroff |first=Perri |work=Screen Rant |date=April 20, 2013 |accessdate=April 20, 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130422075237/http://screenrant.com/agent-coulson-shield-role-avengers-death-return/ |archivedate=April 22, 2013 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"GreggRebuilding\">{{cite web |title=Rebuilding S.H.I.E.L.D. With Clark Gregg |url=http://marvel.com/news/tv/23311/rebuilding_shield_with_clark_gregg |last=Strom |first=Marc |publisher=[[Marvel Comics|Marvel.com]] |date=September 22, 2014 |accessdate=November 15, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6U5WKszcN?url=http://marvel.com/news/tv/23311/rebuilding_shield_with_clark_gregg |archivedate=November 14, 2014 |url-status=dead  }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"GreggHitFixJan2014\">{{cite web|url=http://www.hitfix.com/the-fien-print/interview-clark-gregg-teases-agents-of-shield-evolution-and-coulsons-secret |title=Interview: Clark Gregg Teases 'Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.' Evolution and Coulson's Secret |last=Fienberg |first=Daniel |publisher=HitFix |date=January 7, 2014 |accessdate=November 15, 2014 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6U5cn8DIb?url=http://www.hitfix.com/the-fien-print/interview-clark-gregg-teases-agents-of-shield-evolution-and-coulsons-secret |archivedate=November 14, 2014 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"GreggCBRJan2015\">{{cite web |url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=58514 |title=Clark Gregg Talks Launching Inhumans on \"Agents of SHIELD\" |last=Huver |first=Scott |publisher=Comic Book Resources |date=January 16, 2015 |accessdate=January 19, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Vh27MzyN?url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=58514 |archivedate=January 19, 2015 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"GreggJan2016\">{{cite web|url=https://www.denofgeek.com/tv/clark-gregg/35927/clark-gregg-interview-marvel-shield-civil-war |title=Clark Gregg interview: Marvel, S.H.I.E.L.D., Civil War |last=Leane |first=Rob |publisher=[[Den of Geek]] |date=January 11, 2016 |accessdate=January 11, 2016 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eSsjJK8g?url=http://www.denofgeek.com/tv/clark-gregg/35927/clark-gregg-